text: Nicolae Munteanu (born 6 December 1931) is a Romanian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Romania Category:Ski jumpers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
